elements.name: As a user I make the site private

steps.name: I set scenario "Manage_settings_make_private" and version app "<VERSION>"
I enter "<USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having xpath "(//a[@class='ember-view'])[8]"
I click on element having xpath "//span[@class='input-toggle-component']"
I click on element having xpath "//button[@class='gh-btn gh-btn-blue gh-btn-icon ember-view']"
I verify "A private RSS feed is available at" into field having xpath "//span[@class='avoid-break-out']"
